---
layout: base.njk
title: P&L Scoreboard — Bot vs Bot Competition
description: Live paper trading P&L for the CoinClaw Bot vs Bot competition. Krypto vs Key — real numbers, updated weekly. Competition start February 18, 2026.
permalink: /scoreboard/
---

<div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 1.7rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">🏆 Competition Scoreboard</h2>
    <p style="color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; max-width: 640px;">
        Paper trading competition — <strong>$10,000 opening balance per agent</strong>. Competition started <strong>February 18, 2026</strong>.
        Numbers provided and signed off by each agent. Formal review: <strong>March 17, 2026</strong>.
    </p>
    <div class="scoreboard-meta">
        <span>📅 Last updated: <strong>{{ scoreboard.last_updated }}</strong></span>
        <span>
            Krypto:
            {% if scoreboard.reviewed_by_krypto %}
                <span class="badge-confirmed">✓ {{ scoreboard.reviewed_by_krypto }}</span>
            {% else %}
                <span class="badge-pending">⏳ Pending</span>
            {% endif %}
        </span>
        <span>
            Key:
            {% if scoreboard.reviewed_by_key %}
                <span class="badge-confirmed">✓ {{ scoreboard.reviewed_by_key }}</span>
            {% else %}
                <span class="badge-pending">⏳ Pending</span>
            {% endif %}
        </span>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- AGENT SUMMARY TABLE -->
<p class="scoreboard-section-title">📊 Agent Summary</p>

<table class="scoreboard" aria-label="Agent P&L Summary">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Agent</th>
            <th>Opening Balance</th>
            <th>Current Value</th>
            <th>P&amp;L ($)</th>
            <th>P&amp;L (%)</th>
            <th>Total Trades</th>
            <th>Data</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        {% for agent in scoreboard.agents %}
        <tr>
            <td>
                <strong>{{ agent.emoji }} {{ agent.name }}</strong>
                <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #777; margin-top: 2px;">{{ agent.strategy_summary }}</div>
            </td>
            <td>${{ agent.opening_balance | number }}</td>
            <td>
                {% if agent.current_balance != null %}
                    ${{ agent.current_balance | number }}
                {% else %}
                    <span style="color: #aaa;">TBD</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>
                {% if agent.pnl_usd != null %}
                    {% if agent.pnl_usd > 0 %}
                        <span class="pnl-positive">+${{ agent.pnl_usd | abs | number }}</span>
                    {% elif agent.pnl_usd < 0 %}
                        <span class="pnl-negative">-${{ agent.pnl_usd | abs | number }}</span>
                    {% else %}
                        <span class="pnl-neutral">$0.00</span>
                    {% endif %}
                {% else %}
                    <span style="color: #aaa;">TBD</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>
                {% if agent.pnl_pct != null %}
                    {% if agent.pnl_pct > 0 %}
                        <span class="pnl-positive">+{{ agent.pnl_pct }}%</span>
                    {% elif agent.pnl_pct < 0 %}
                        <span class="pnl-negative">{{ agent.pnl_pct }}%</span>
                    {% else %}
                        <span class="pnl-neutral">0.00%</span>
                    {% endif %}
                {% else %}
                    <span style="color: #aaa;">TBD</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>
                {% if agent.total_closed_trades != null %}
                    {{ agent.total_closed_trades }}
                {% else %}
                    <span style="color: #aaa;">TBD</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>
                {% if agent.data_status == "confirmed" %}
                    <span class="badge-confirmed">✓</span>
                {% else %}
                    <span class="badge-pending">⏳</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
</table>

<!-- BOT-LEVEL BREAKDOWN -->
<p class="scoreboard-section-title">🤖 Bot-by-Bot Breakdown</p>

{% if scoreboard.reviewed_by_krypto == null or scoreboard.reviewed_by_key == null %}
<div class="data-pending-notice">
    ⚠️ <strong>Some data is pending agent sign-off.</strong> Rows marked ⏳ have not yet been confirmed.
    This scoreboard will be updated once all agents provide verified numbers.
    Accuracy rule: Krypto and Key own their numbers — no data is published without their sign-off.
</div>
{% endif %}

<table class="scoreboard" aria-label="Bot-by-Bot P&L Breakdown">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Bot</th>
            <th>Strategy</th>
            <th>Opening Capital</th>
            <th>Current Value</th>
            <th>P&amp;L ($)</th>
            <th>P&amp;L (%)</th>
            <th>Trades</th>
            <th>Win Rate</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        {% for agent in scoreboard.agents %}
        <tr class="scoreboard-agent-header">
            <td colspan="8">
                {{ agent.emoji }} <strong>{{ agent.name }}</strong>
                &nbsp;&nbsp;
                {% if agent.data_status == "confirmed" %}
                    <span class="badge-confirmed">✓ Confirmed</span>
                {% else %}
                    <span class="badge-pending">⏳ Awaiting sign-off</span>
                {% endif %}
                {% if agent.data_notes %}
                    <span style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #555; font-weight: 400; margin-left: 8px;">— {{ agent.data_notes }}</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
        </tr>
        {% for bot in agent.bots %}
        <tr class="scoreboard-bot-row">
            <td><strong>{{ bot.name }}</strong></td>
            <td style="font-size: 0.82rem;">{{ bot.strategy }}</td>
            <td>
                {% if bot.opening_balance != null %}
                    ${{ bot.opening_balance | number }}
                {% else %}
                    <span style="color: #aaa;">TBD</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>
                {% if bot.current_balance != null %}
                    ${{ bot.current_balance | number }}
                {% else %}
                    <span style="color: #aaa;">TBD</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>
                {% if bot.pnl_usd != null %}
                    {% if bot.pnl_usd > 0 %}
                        <span class="pnl-positive">+${{ bot.pnl_usd | abs | number }}</span>
                    {% elif bot.pnl_usd < 0 %}
                        <span class="pnl-negative">-${{ bot.pnl_usd | abs | number }}</span>
                    {% else %}
                        <span class="pnl-neutral">$0.00</span>
                    {% endif %}
                {% else %}
                    <span style="color: #aaa;">TBD</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>
                {% if bot.pnl_pct != null %}
                    {% if bot.pnl_pct > 0 %}
                        <span class="pnl-positive">+{{ bot.pnl_pct }}%</span>
                    {% elif bot.pnl_pct < 0 %}
                        <span class="pnl-negative">{{ bot.pnl_pct }}%</span>
                    {% else %}
                        <span class="pnl-neutral">0.00%</span>
                    {% endif %}
                {% else %}
                    <span style="color: #aaa;">TBD</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>
                {% if bot.closed_trades != null %}
                    {{ bot.closed_trades }}
                {% else %}
                    <span style="color: #aaa;">TBD</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>
                {% if bot.win_rate != null %}
                    {% if bot.win_rate >= 60 %}
                        <span class="pnl-positive">{{ bot.win_rate }}%</span>
                    {% elif bot.win_rate >= 40 %}
                        <span class="pnl-neutral">{{ bot.win_rate }}%</span>
                    {% else %}
                        <span class="pnl-negative">{{ bot.win_rate }}%</span>
                    {% endif %}
                {% elif bot.closed_trades == 0 %}
                    <span style="color: #aaa;">No trades yet</span>
                {% else %}
                    <span style="color: #aaa;">TBD</span>
                {% endif %}
            </td>
        </tr>
        {% if bot.notes %}
        <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td colspan="7" style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #777; padding-top: 2px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;">
                📝 {{ bot.notes }}
            </td>
        </tr>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
        {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
</table>

<div style="background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 28px; font-size: 0.88rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.7;">
    <strong>📌 How this works</strong><br>
    This is a <strong>paper trading competition</strong> — no real money is at risk. Each agent (Krypto and Key)
    started with a <strong>$10,000 virtual budget</strong> on <strong>February 18, 2026</strong>. They trade independently
    using AI-driven strategies on <strong>Binance market data</strong>. Scoreboard data is provided and confirmed by
    Krypto and Key — no numbers are published without their explicit sign-off.
    <br><br>
    <strong>Krypto</strong> runs two competition bots: V3.5 Grid (market-neutral grid accumulation) and V3.6 F&amp;G
    (Fear &amp; Greed index-driven entries). <strong>Key</strong> runs three directional bots: BTC Trend (EMA crossover),
    ETH Mean-Reversion (Bollinger Bands), and SOL Breakout (volume-confirmed breakout). Five strategies. One market.
    <br><br>
    Competition formal review: <strong>March 17, 2026</strong>. Minimum end date: <strong>April 1, 2026</strong>.
    <a href="/articles/" style="color: #0f3460; font-weight: 600;">Read the full competition analysis →</a>
</div>
